def calculate_wonder_sum(string: str) -> int:
    MOD = 1000000008
    start = (ord(string[0]) - 96) * 100
    wonder_sum = 0
    for char in string:
        wonder_sum += start + (ord(char) - 97)
    return wonder_sum % MOD
